# Environment Configuration

## Local environment file

- The local environment file is `web/.env.local`
- All database operations (drizzle-kit generate, migrate, studio) read from `.env.local`
- NEVER commit `.env.local` to git
- When running drizzle-kit commands, run them from the `web/` directory so they pick up `.env.local`

## Key environment variables

- `DATABASE_URL` — Postgres connection string (Neon)
- `AUTH_GOOGLE_ID` / `AUTH_GOOGLE_SECRET` — Google OAuth
- `AUTH_MICROSOFT_ENTRA_ID_ID` / `AUTH_MICROSOFT_ENTRA_ID_SECRET` — Microsoft OAuth
- `AUTH_SECRET` — NextAuth secret

